{"type":"text","timestamp":1781134826262,"sessionID":"ses_14c2280dbffe6wVUIz1f6LQA8s","part":{"id":"prt_eb3e89ac7001tojf12x25C0Boi","messageID":"msg_eb3e84689001l9gMOrRBivGyye","sessionID":"ses_14c2280dbffe6wVUIz1f6LQA8s","type":"text","text":"The user's request has been fully addressed with the creation of a temperature conversion module (temperature_conversion.py), corresponding unit tests (test_conversions.py), a command-line tool (cli.py), tests for the CLI (test_cli.py), and documentation (cli_usage.md). All required components are present in the file structure.","time":{"start":1781134826183,"end":1781134826260}}}
